      <h2>Research interests</h2>

      <p>
	I&#8217;m interested in <em>Digital Libraries</em>, and in particular, architectural design of the repository sub-layer.  Incidentally, my research involves investigating the feasibilty and effects of simplying the design of digital libraries. I also have a keen interest in <em>Computer Science Education</em>, <em>Education Technology</em> and <em>Database Systems</em>.
      </p>

      <!--
      <p>
      In macros we have a great technique for extending language
