      <h2>Publications</h2>

      <ul class="bib">
        <li><a href="http://www.icadl2012.org/AcceptedPapersandPosters.html#01">Bonolo: A General Digital Library System for File-based Collections</a> (with <a
	  href="http://people.cs.uct.ac.za/~kwilliams" target="_blank">Kyle Williams</a>, <a href="http://people.cs.uct.ac.za/~mrobinson" target="_blank">Miles Robinson</a>, <a href="http://people.cs.uct.ac.za/~shammar" target="_blank">Stuart Hammar</a> and <a href="http://www.husseinsspace.com" target="_blank">Hussein Suleman</a>).
      <em>In Proceedings of the 14th International Conference on Asia-Pacific Digital Libraries
      (ICADL&rsquo;12)</em>,
      November 2012
        </li>

        <li><a href="http://pubs.cs.uct.ac.za/archive/00000780/" target="_blank">In Search of Simplicity: Redesigning the Digital Bleek and Lloyd</a> (with <a
	href="http://www.husseinsspace.com" target="_blank">Hussein Suleman</a>).
      <em>Published in DESIDOC Journal of Library &amp; Information Technology
      (DJIT)</em>,
      July 2012
        </li>
	
        <li><a href="http://dl.cs.uct.ac.za/node/147" target="_blank">SimplyCT: A Lightweight Digital Library Framework</a> (with <a href="http://www.husseinsspace.com" target="_blank">Hussein Suleman</a>).
      In <em>SAICSIT Postgraduate Symposium
      (SAICSIT&rsquo;11)</em>,
      September 2011
        </li>
      </ul>

